properties.areaDesc: San Luis Obispo County Central Coast
properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued January 5 at 8:18PM PST until January 6 at 9:00AM PST by NWS Los Angeles/Oxnard CA
properties.description:
* WHAT...Areas of northeast winds 15 to 30 mph with gusts up to 40
mph.

* WHERE...San Luis Obispo County Central Coast.

* WHEN...From midnight tonight to 9 AM PST Monday.

* IMPACTS...Gusty winds will blow around unsecured objects and
make driving difficult, especially for high profile vehicles.
Tree limbs could be blown down and a few power outages may
result.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Travel may be affected on Highways 1 and
101.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM MIDNIGHT TONIGHT TO 9 AM PST MONDAY
